title: Simon Green-Live and Let Drood
description: The New York Times best-selling author of the Nightside series, Simon R. Green has won widespread acclaim and an immense following for his Secret Histories novels featuring Eddie "Shaman Bond" Drood. In Green's action-packed riff on everyone's favorite superspy, Eddie once again finds himself at the center of supernatural intrigue. And even though protecting humanity from the forces of darkness is nothing new to Eddie, he now faces a threat that'sleaving him both shaken and stirred.
